WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
I did it all for you.

2
00:00:03.180 --> 00:00:15.039
But Dad, Damien, what are they doing?

3
00:00:17.410 --> 00:00:20.129
Your father is asking my son for money again.

4
00:00:20.769 --> 00:00:22.690
This isn't the first time I ever look at Asha.

5
00:00:23.410 --> 00:00:25.730
I need to talk to Damien about this.

6
00:00:25.730 --> 00:00:27.170
About what exactly?

7
00:00:27.170 --> 00:00:29.570
Haven't you and your father done enough?

8
00:00:29.570 --> 00:00:32.210
How long are you going to keep dragging him down like this?

9
00:00:32.929 --> 00:00:42.320
Ah, this is an internship offer from the best airline in Switzerland that he declined.

10
00:00:43.039 --> 00:00:53.840
He gave up a promising career because of you.

11
00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:57.359
But also if you kept from me, what does it matter anymore?

12
00:00:57.359 --> 00:01:00.289
You love him, let him go.

13
00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:11.599
What you said was really harsh.

14
00:01:12.480 --> 00:01:13.680
Is this really even worth it?

15
00:01:15.170 --> 00:01:16.769
Thank you for your help, Taylor.

16
00:01:17.650 --> 00:01:19.250
But I just want to be a mom.

17
00:01:19.250 --> 00:01:56.939
I'm scared.

